        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">Near<placeName> Hartland Wisc.</placeName>__</p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><date>Nov: 29<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1851</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <addressee>Rev. I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I had the pleasure of <sic>receiveing</sic><lb/> two of your
                periodical the “Occident” for <date>Nov</date> &amp; <date>Dec</date>—<lb/> on which
                acct you find enclosed fifty cents.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">By return of mail please forward to my address<lb/> any (3) three
                volumes containing <hi rend="underline">12</hi> numbers each of your “Occident”<lb/>
                if this can be done at (5) <hi rend="underline">five dollars including
                postage</hi>.<lb/> (and suppose it would be sent in three diff parcels on acct<lb/>
                of weights.) I hope circumstances will allow me<lb/> later to subscribe &amp;
                receive <add>?</add> all your writings but<lb/> presently I can not well spare more
                money for this purpose</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">By sending me the required three volumes you will<lb/> oblige me and
                on receipt of the same I shall be happy to send<lb/> the amount of five dollars to
                you if need for <hi rend="underline">your</hi><lb/><hi rend="underline">risk</hi> or
                you may cash the same by the Postmasters here.<lb/> In any case I expect a few here
                as an answer to this<lb/> letter before the <date>20th</date> next month
                    <del>forwarded to me</del></p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">Yours most respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <persName role="author">Charles Balaud</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2V"/>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <placeName>Hartland Wis</placeName>
                <hi rend="indent(3)">Paid 6</hi>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">No 14 <date>Nov 29</date></p>
            <p rend="indent(5)"><addressee>Revd. Mr I. Leeser</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <placeName>371 Walnut street</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Editor of the “Occident=</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <add>?</add>
                <hi rend="indent(3)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</hi>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <placeName>Pa</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="The following is written in pencil at the top right corner."> Web 3/00 #50<lb/>
                #001 5/99<lb/> Rare Frontier<lb/> Judaica<lb/> possibly rare Postal<lb/> also</p>
        </body>
